<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.1.3">
<l>parañcōti nīparamāy niṉṉikaḻntu piṉmaṟṟōr</l>
<l>parañcōti yiṉmaiyiṉ paṭiyōvi niḻalkiṉṟa</l>
<l>parañcōti niṉṉuḷḷē paṭarulakam paṭaittavem</l>
<l>parañcōti kōvintā paṇpuraikka māṭṭēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with highest light being the highest, in the absence of any other</l>
<l>highest light after, belittling you, I cannot speak you [your] quality</l>
<l>o Govinda, our highest light, who created the spreading world</l>
<l>inside yourself with highest light that stops [and] shine on the earth.</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
